Title: Bucks spoil Chris Finch’s Timberwolves debut
Description: MILWAUKEE — Giannis Antetokoumpo had 37 points, eight rebounds and eight assists as the Milwaukee Bucks beat Minnesota 139-112 on Tuesday to spoil Timberwolves coach Chris Finch’s debut. Antetokounmpo put up those numbers in just 29 minutes.
Author: Fox Sports
